Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 17:20:12 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 19/19] feat(api): create-time model selection and
 /v1/providers catalog

Session create endpoints (/v1/sessions chat+worktree, /api/sessions) now
accept an explicit model + provider selection, resolved through the same
switch_model pipeline as the session /model command and stored in session
model_config so every future turn runs on the requested model.

Adds GET /v1/providers exposing the authenticated-provider catalog
(list_authenticated_providers) with current model/provider, filtered
through the model_picker.allow whitelist
(load_model_picker_filter/apply_model_picker_filter) so external UIs
(the desktop model selector) mirror the curated TUI picker exactly.

